                  <h4 class="subheading">Check out EventHop Polls and Chatrooms</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">Compare your Step 1 selections to what others at EventHop have chosen. You'll be able to see what else is popular in the EventHop community. Now with EventHop's chatrooms you are able to chat with other event goers in real-time. Of course when you're done you'll want to take a look at online reviews and your event choice's websites . . .</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="public/img/about/3.jpeg" alt="">
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>Step 3</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading">Don't Forget about Reviews and Websites</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">EventHop makes the searching easy. Our custom analytics helps provide you with top options to streamline planning your events. No more pouring through Internet searches for something to do, all of the information has already been done!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="public/img/about/4.jpg" alt="">
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>Step 4</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading">Print, Save, Email, Text, or Message your Itenerary</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">Final step! Now that EventHop has helped you with your event planning, don't forget to keep those directions! We hope that EventHop has saved you time, effort, and frustration by using our free services. We understand that your time is precious and that planning an event can be tedious. Hopefully you like our services and will return to plan your future events!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="public/img/about/5.png" alt="">
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-panel">
                <div class="timeline-heading">
                  <h4>Step 5 (Optional)</h4>
                  <h4 class="subheading">Pay it Forward</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-body">
                  <p class="text-muted">EventHop is a completely free service for members and their guests and we will never ask money for our services. We care about our local community and believe in connecting people with local events. We also believe in giving back. If you would like to donate to a local charity then we have made this a little easier too!</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="timeline-inverted">
              <div class="timeline-image">
                <h4>Volunteer Time
